From bbd640562d181a607fdef50d6049aec0a0811ad6 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Balamurugan Ramar <quic_bramar@quicinc.com>
Date: Thu, 10 Apr 2025 23:26:17 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] mac80211: athk Set correct tx_bw when EHT OP is present

Allow correct phymode to be set when
EHT320 is present.

Signed-off-by: Ramanathan Choodamani <quic_rchoodam@quicinc.com>
Signed-off-by: Balamurugan Ramar <quic_bramar@quicinc.com>
---
 net/mac80211/vht.c | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/net/mac80211/vht.c b/net/mac80211/vht.c
index 5b5a01c..6e6ca31 100644
--- a/net/mac80211/vht.c
+++ b/net/mac80211/vht.c
@@ -366,7 +366,7 @@ __ieee80211_sta_cap_rx_bw(struct link_sta_info *link_sta,
 		 * to advertise the 320MHz support. Removind band
 		 * specific check for now.
 		 */
-		if (eht_cap->has_eht && band != NL80211_BAND_6GHZ) {
+		if (eht_cap->has_eht && band != NL80211_BAND_2GHZ) {
 			info = eht_cap->eht_cap_elem.phy_cap_info[0];
 
 			if (info & IEEE80211_EHT_PHY_CAP0_320MHZ_IN_6GHZ)
-- 
2.34.1

